              <thead><tr><th>Command</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>!stoatcord code</code></td><td>Generate a one-time migration claim code (admin)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>!stoatcord request &lt;guild_id&gt;</code></td><td>Send a live migration approval request to Discord</td></tr>
